# FireReach — Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` in project root and fill in your values.
The backend loads these via Render.com environment variables (not .env in production).

```env
# ── LLM APIs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GROQ_API_KEY=            # https://console.groq.com — free, 14,400 req/day
GEMINI_API_KEY=          # https://aistudio.google.com — free, 1,500 req/day

# ── Signal APIs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SERPER_API_KEY=          # https://serper.dev — free, 2,500 searches/mo
TAVILY_API_KEY=          # https://tavily.com — free, 1,000 searches/mo
BUILTWITH_API_KEY=free   # Free tier key — literally the string "free"
NEWS_API_KEY=            # newsapi.org — free 100 req/day, optional — Tavily is used as fallback if this is not set

# ── Contact Resolution ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
APOLLO_API_KEY=          # apollo.io free tier — 95 credits per month, uses contacts/search endpoint
HUNTER_API_KEY=          # https://hunter.io → Pricing → Free (25 searches/mo)
SNOVIO_CLIENT_ID=        # https://snov.io → API → free (50 credits/mo) — optional
SNOVIO_CLIENT_SECRET=    # same as above — optional

# ── Email Dispatch ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GMAIL_FROM=                # Your Gmail address e.g. you@gmail.com
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=        # 16-character app password from myaccount.google.com under Security then App Passwords
UNSUB_EMAIL=unsubscribe@mail.yourdomain.com

# ── Database ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
SUPABASE_URL=            # https://app.supabase.com → Project Settings → API
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=    # Service role key (not anon key) — keep secret

# ── CORS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,https://your-frontend.vercel.app

# ── N8N (if self-hosting) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
FIREREACH_API_URL=https://firereach-api.onrender.com
DEFAULT_ICP=We sell cloud security to Series B SaaS companies...
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=        # optional — your Telegram chat ID for notifications
SHEETS_DOC_ID=           # optional — Google Sheets document ID for logging
```
